Class Flight

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • seng202.group6.model.Record

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer

    public class Flight
extends Record
implements java.util.Observer
    Represents a flight path between several points. The first and last FlightPoints in the internal collection are expected to represent airports.
